Package: cah
Title: Useful tools for CAHers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jan", "Lindemans", , "janwillem.lindemans@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3702-8651"))
Description: The `cah` package contains useful tools for CAHers. Some tools help with statistical analysis (e.g., CAH-themed plots), other tools make collaboration easier (e.g., computer-agnostic paths), and there's more (e.g., impact estimates and power calculations for health nudges).
